---
title: Mini Beef & Pork Kofta Kebabs with Wedges, Garlic-Yoghurt Dip & Cucumber Salad
description: What can beat a kebab? Nothing much, especially when you can make your own in four easy steps. They’re unstoppable with delicious seasoned beef and pork koftas, a hummus and garlic yoghurt with a side of wedges. You’ll be seeing more kebabs on the menu in the future.

